<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@sonnyp:matrix.org">sonnyp</a> announces</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://apps.gnome.org/app/re.sonny.Commit/">Commit message editor</a> now use GtkSourceView which allows for new features and improvements. It&rsquo;s also now <a href="https://hosted.weblate.org/engage/commit/">available to translate on Weblate</a>.

<img src="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2022/01/twig-26/JHctHlBdscsvjjQVpNOuUBAU.png" alt="" />
