<blockquote>
<p>The app pages on <a href="https://apps.gnome.org">apps.gnome.org</a> are now coming with a more exciting header design. Further, page rendering times have been optimized and a few issues with right-to-left scripts have been fixed. The latter surfaced with the newly added Hebrew translation.

